channel.title: An error when obfusticating
channel.description:
Exception in thread "Thread-5" java.lang.ClassCastException: com.zelix.ks at com.zelix.zd.a(zd.java:118) at com.zelix.vm.a(vm.java:1379) at com.zelix.vm.a(vm.java:712) at com.zelix.vm.<init>(vm.java:1202) at com.zelix.du.a(du.java:847) at com.zelix.du.a(du.java:715) at com.zelix.du.a(du.java:813) at com.zelix.rt.a(rt.java:12) at com.zelix.ou.a(ou.java:105) at com.zelix.mt.a(mt.java:167) at com.zelix.it.a(it.java:330) at com.zelix.it.a(it.java:1785) at com.zelix.xr.run(xr.java:67) at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source)
I used zelik klassmaster and each time I get that error. I'm trying to obfusticate a .jar file (contains .class files).
I jarred the file with this: jar cf xxxx.jar *.class
Any ideas? Or suggestions? Or anyone suggest another obfusticater?
Also, if anyone has a MC 203 (RSC) just-a-client could they upload it for me also please?
